ext-slate-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-1">VALOR LÍQUIDO</p><h2 className="text-3xl font-black text-slate-900 tracking-tighter leading-none">{formatMoney(totalToPay)}</h2></div></div>)}</div>
